  <brief_title>Randomized Trial on Adjuvant Chemotherapy in Colon Carcinoma Dukes B</brief_title>
  <official_title>A Prospectively Randomized Study on Adjuvant Chemotherapy in Patients With Operated Colon Carcinoma Dukes B (Stage II; T3-4, N0, M0).</official_title>
  <sponsors>
