  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This clinical investigation examined the influence of cytostatic chemotherapy with
      5-fluorouracil, modulated by biologically active leucovorin, on patientsâ€™ survival time
      following surgery for colon carcinoma Stage II.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
